## Conclusion  
By combining robust audio processing with on-device ML and adaptive difficulty algorithms, this project aims to elevate “Scream Go Hero” from a novelty into a polished, inclusive gaming experience. The integration of AI/ML not only addresses the original’s technical limitations but also showcases the potential of intelligent systems to enhance interactive entertainment. The methodology and outcomes will serve as a reference for future voice-controlled game development, emphasizing accessibility and player-centric design.

